Respawn Anchor=Renaskiĝa Ankro
The respawn anchor is a block that allows the player to set their spawn point in the Nether. It will only work if fueled using glowstone blocks.=
Use a glowstone block to add a charge.=
Respawn anchors can be charged up to four times. Rightclick on a charged anchor to set a new spawn point.=
A respawn anchor only works in the Nether. Attempting to use a charged anchor to set a new spawn point outside the Nether will cause it to explode.=
